title: Grateful Dead Live at Cumberland County Civic Center on 1983-10-18
description:
Set I
Jack Straw
They Love Each Other
Me & My Uncle >
Mexicali Blues
Dupree's Diamond Blues
C.C. Rider
Althea
Lazy Lightning >
Supplication >
Might As Well
Set II
China Cat Sunflower >
I Know You Rider

He's Gone >
Drums >
Space >
Not Fade Away >
Black Peter >
Around & Around >
Sugar Magnolia

Encore:
U.S. Blues


Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
